m\": \"offers\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"The Independent\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice Kimberley Woods'Olympic bronze medal-winning redemptiontook less than 150 seconds to confirm, but the wait felt like an eternity for the Rugby kayaker.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.8318640603567028, \"rank\": 0.2020781438112283, \"text\": \"Kimberley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wait\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"an eternity\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rugby kayaker\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old, who three summers ago in Tokyo was visibly distraught after incurring 56 seconds worth of penalties for a bottom finish in her maiden Olympic final, was sitting in third position with just one competitor left who could knock her off the Paris podium - defending champion Ricarda Funk, the fastest finisher from the afternoon's semis.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.993314368749067, \"rank\": 0.006730626656854149, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992446647, \"rank\": 7.555110404302406e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricarda_Funk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ricarda Funk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricarda_Funk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ricarda_Funk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"penalties\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"a bottom finish\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"her maiden Olympic final\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"third position\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"just one competitor\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest finisher\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"the afternoon's semis\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the German made a mistake at the bottom of the course a 50-second penalty to finish 11th in 149.08, ensuring Woods' 98.94 was good enough for her first Olympic medal behind first-placed Australian Jessica Fox and Poland's Klaudia Zwolinska, who snuck into silver with the penultimate run.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9984934569015992, \"rank\": 0.0013931241154972022, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9994785036467301, \"rank\": 0.0003814121225424987, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\", \"score\": 0.548202986974713, \"rank\": 0.8241415192508661, \"text\": \"Jessica Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Fox_(actress)\"}, {\"begin\": 1170, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"score\": 0.7912768952934301, \"rank\": 0.25519830024620693, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_men's_national_volleyball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 996}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"a 50-second penalty\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"the penultimate run\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods said: \\\"It feels absolutely incredible.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not believe how long my journey's been.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been paddling for 20 years now and finally have a medal around my neck.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 years\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"my neck\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ricarda Funk coming down, I could not watch.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1463, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ricarda Funk\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was on my knees, I was head in hands not being able to watch and all of a sudden I heard the crowd shout something and there was a mistake and I was like, 'oh my god, I can not believe I have done it.'\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my knees\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"hands\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That whole journey of where I have come from in the last 10 years has been incredible.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That whole journey\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 10 years\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really proud of who I am today, being able to be open and speak, use my platform for good.\\\"\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my platform\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods has been candid about her long-term struggles with mental health and self-harm, and twice checking into private mental health hospital the Priory and admitting to experiencing suicidal thoughts at her lowest points.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"her long-term struggles\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"self-harm\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"private mental health hospital\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"the Priory\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"suicidal thoughts\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"her lowest points\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview with theGuardian, the paddler, who was introduced to the sport by her aunt Diane - a silver medallist at the 1994 World Junior Championships - Woods revealed she had not harmed herself since after a race just before the TokyoOlympics.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2169, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diane_Chambers\", \"score\": 0.9999998161161043, \"rank\": 1.66675844056447e-07, \"text\": \"Diane\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diane_Chambers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diane_Chambers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"theGuardian\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the paddler\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medallist\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1994 World Junior Championships - Woods\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"the TokyoOlympics\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her first Olympic medal glittering around her neck, Woods reflected that, compared to her most challenging times, managing the darkest points of her internal battles, the bronze medal moment \\\"makes everything worth it.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"her neck\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2392}, {\"ngram\": \"her most challenging times\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"the darkest points\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"her internal battles\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal moment\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The journey I have been on, that first moment of admitting that I do need help, that's where I go back to.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that first moment\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's okay to do that, it's okay to seek out help with the people that are close to me.\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always been trying to be open with my coach of where I am at because I see him more than anyone else in my family.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am still getting help today, topping up the toolbox and making sure I still have the skills to deal with whatever the Games has but also whatever life has.\\\"\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"the toolbox\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"the skills\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2969}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever life\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Woods bounced back in the years following her Tokyo heartbreak, claiming a bronze medal at the World Championships later in 2021, 10 days after she was involved in a car crash.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3082, \"end\": 3087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.993314368749067, \"rank\": 0.006730626656854149, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Woods\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3067}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"a car crash\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In September, she claimed her first world title in kayak cross on home turf at the ICF Canoe Slalom World Championships in Lee Valley, where she also took C1 silver alongside gold and bronze in the C1 and K1 team events.\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3265, \"end\": 3270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.9999978655164384, \"rank\": 2.1344860886661304e-06, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}, {\"begin\": 3337, \"end\": 3347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Valley_White_Water_Centre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7816355390693378e-20, \"text\": \"Lee Valley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Valley_White_Water_Centre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Valley_White_Water_Centre\"}, {\"begin\": 3369, \"end\": 3371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9999999680121624, \"rank\": 3.1987997258555024e-08, \"text\": \"C1\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 3412, \"end\": 3414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9999999680121624, \"rank\": 3.1987997258555024e-08, \"text\": \"C1\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 3419, \"end\": 3421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.3375778819994301e-12, \"text\": \"K1\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"her first world title\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3261}, {\"ngram\": \"home turf\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"the ICF\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"Canoe Slalom World Championships\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3389, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday she will have a second crack at gold, this time in the event in which she is world champion, with kayak cross making its Olympic debut atParis 2024.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3544, \"end\": 3549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"score\": 0.9999978655164384, \"rank\": 2.1344860886661304e-06, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3445}, {\"ngram\": \"a second crack\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3474}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"world champion\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3537}, {\"ngram\": \"its Olympic debut\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For now, though slalom superfan Woods, who cannot wait to watch her team-mates in competition, said: \\\"I am kind of glad that I have got four days off just to chill out.\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"slalom superfan Woods\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3633}, {\"ngram\": \"her team-mates\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3674}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am used to the (atmosphere) now.\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the (atmosphere\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am probably maybe one of the favourites in the kayak cross but I am not thinking about that, I am just thinking about being out there and enjoying the crowd, and I can not wait to sit on top of that ramp.\\\"\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 4009, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the favourites\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3843}, {\"ngram\": \"the kayak cross\", \"from\": 3847, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 3960}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 3994}, {\"ngram\": \"that ramp\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4062, \"end\": 4073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8801005675900787e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 4016, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 4090, \"to\": 4103}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4127}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4155}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 4159, \"to\": 4167}, {\"ngram\": \"inP